						<summary>

						<p>On a hero-stone set up on the tank bund.</p>						

						<p>Circa 12th century.</p>						

						<p>It seems to record the death of Nāga-gāvuṇḍa in a fight on the occasion of a cattle raid. The inscription is damaged and worn out.</p>						

						</summary>
